msgid ""
"The *Diffuse* :abbr:`BSDF (Bidirectional scattering distribution "
"function)` node is used to add Lambertian and Oren-Nayar diffuse "
"reflection."
msgstr ""
"Le node *Diffuse* :abbr:`BSDF (Bidirectional scattering distribution "
"function)` est utilisé pour ajouter la réflexion *Lambertian* et *Oren-"
"Nayar diffuse*. "

